<!--Frequently Asked Questions -->
<h1 class="ttl_faq">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

<!--FAQ subtitle/welcome text-->
<h5 class="subttl_faq">Hey there! We know you have many questions, so we're here to help. If you can't find any of the answers
					  to your questions on this page, you can always <%=link_to "contact us", "#" %>, and we will do our
					  best to help you out! 
</h5>
<!--Question response goes here -->
<h4 class="hd_question"> What are the benefits of using Pidgin over normal food delivery?</h4>
<h5 class="hd_response"> There are tons of benefits to using Pidgin over normal food delivery services!
						 Our main benefits include lower-priced food delivery, lower wait time, and a 
						 healthier environmental impact!
</h5>
<!--Question/Response goes here -->
<h4 class="hd_question"> When will you launch?</h4>
<h5 class="hd_response"> We plan to begin testing in specific areas in 2019, and officially release in 2021.
</h5>
<!--Question/Response goes here -->
<h4 class="hd_question"> How does Pidgin work?</h4>
<h5 class="hd_response"> Simple! You place an order on our app just like any other delivery service. Then, a loader will get your 
						 order send it off to you in one of our drones. Our drones will safely fly over traffic and deliver it to 
						 you in an open space - all within minutes.
</h5>
<!--Question/Response goes here -->
<h4 class="hd_question"> When can I order through Pidgin?</h4>
<h5 class="hd_response"> During our testing period there will be limited areas where you can order Pidgin only during daytime.
						 Once we officially launch in 2021 we plan to be offering drone delivery 24/7.
</h5>
